#. Type: title
#. Description
#. Info message displayed when running in rescue mode
#: ../rescue-check.templates:11
#, fuzzy
msgid "Rescue mode"
msgstr "Defnyddio'r modd arbed"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:3
msgid "Enter rescue mode"
msgstr "Defnyddio'r modd arbed"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:8
msgid "Device to mount as root file system:"
msgstr "Y ddyfais i'w glymu fel y system ffeiliau gwraidd:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:8
msgid "Enter a device you wish to mount as your root file system."
msgstr "Rhowch ddyffais y hoffwch glymu fel eich system ffeiliau gwraidd."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:8
msgid ""
"After this message, if the file system was mounted successfully, you will be "
"given a shell with that file system on \"/\". If you need any other file "
"systems (such as a separate \"/usr\"), you will have to mount those yourself."
msgstr ""
"Ar ôl y neges hwn, os clymwyd y system ffeiliau yn llwyddiannus, cewch "
"blisgyn gyda'r system ffeiliau hwnnw ar \"/\". Os ydych angen unrhyw "
"systemau ffeiliau eraill (fel \"/usr\" ar wahan), bydd rhaid i chi eu clymu "
"nhw eich hun."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:20
msgid "No such device"
msgstr "Nid yw'r ddyfais yn bodoli"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:20
msgid ""
"The device you entered for your root file system (${DEVICE}) does not exist. "
"Please try again."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw'r ddyfais fe roddoch ar gyfer eich system ffeiliau gwraidd "
"(${DEVICE}) yn bodoli. Ceisiwch eto."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:26
msgid "Mount failed"
msgstr "Methwyd clymu"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:26
msgid ""
"An error occurred while mounting the device you entered for your root file "
"system (${DEVICE}) on /target."
msgstr ""
"Roedd gwall wrth glymu'r dyfais fe roddoch ar gyfer eich system ffeiliau "
"gwraidd (${DEVICE}) ar /target."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:26
#, fuzzy
msgid "Please check the syslog for more information."
msgstr ""
"Os gwelwch yn dda, gwiriwch y cofnod gwall ar y drydydd consol neu /var/log/"
"messages ar gyfer mwy o wybodaeth."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:34
msgid "No shell found in /target"
msgstr "Dim plisgyn wedi ei ganfod yn /target"

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:34
msgid "No usable shell was found on your root file system (${DEVICE})."
msgstr ""
"Ni chanfuwyd plisgyn defnyddiadwy ar eich system ffeiliau gwraidd "
"(${DEVICE})."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:34
msgid ""
"You will now be given a shell in the installer environment instead. Your "
"root file system is mounted on /target."
msgstr ""
"Cewch nawr blisgyn yn amgylchedd y sefydlydd yn lle. Bydd eich system "
"ffeiliau gwraidd wedi ei glymu ar /target."

#. Type: note
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:34
msgid "When you exit this shell, the system will reboot."
msgstr "Pan rydych chi'n gadael y plisgyn hwn, fe fydd y system yn ailfŵtio."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:45
msgid "Try fallback shell?"
msgstr "Ceisio'r plisgyn wrth gefn?"

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:45
msgid ""
"A shell (${SHELL}) was found on your root file system (${DEVICE}), but an "
"error occurred while running it."
msgstr ""
"Canfuwyd plisgyn (${SHELL}) ar eich system ffeiliau gwraidd (${DEVICE}), ond "
"disgwyddodd gwall wrth ei rhedeg."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:45
msgid ""
"Please confirm whether you want to use a shell in the installer environment "
"instead. Your root file system will be mounted on /target."
msgstr ""
"Cadarnhewch a ydych chi eisiau defnyddio plisgyn yn amgylchedd y sefydlydd "
"yn lle. Caiff eich system ffeiliau gwraidd ei glymu ar /target."

#. Type: boolean
#. Description
#: ../rescue-mode.templates:45
msgid ""
"When you exit this shell, or if you choose not to run it, the system will "
"reboot."
msgstr ""
"Pan rydych chi'n gadael y plisgyn hwn, os ydych chi'n dewis peidio'i rhedeg, "
"fe fydd y system yn ailfŵtio."
